name: Women Fashion Synthetic Leather Handbags Tote Bag Shoulder Bag Top Handle Satchel Purse Set 4pcs
reviews: I normally don’t write reviews much, nor do I write reviews as long as this, so I apologize in advance. But, if you’re considering these sets, it’s worth a read!I absolutely LOVE these bags. Such a great bargain for such great quality, classy/stylish and all around amazing day to day bags/purses. I was incredibly impressed with the delivery/packaging. It wasn’t just thrown in a box. They were in perfectly organized in thin breathable bags (like they’re designer brand or something) they arrived in perfect condition and the bags themselves are very sturdy. Not flimsy at all, they stand on their own and hold quite a bit. I also didn’t realize until it arrived that it matched my key ring perfectly! Down to the tassels and everything.Although,I had only one concern about the smaller bag. The two zippers in the front that meet together with the tassels looked and felt a little sketchy. I didn’t want to pull on the tassels themselves because it felt like the zipper would ruin and tassels would come off. Unfortunately, no matter how safe I tried to be with it, it happened anyway and now is no where to be found, so I’m walking around without. It really disappointed me because, I LOVE this set and have recommended it to just about everyone I know and have shared the link as well to lead everyone where and even bought this for my best friend in a different style/color.*First pic is when they first arrived. The other two are where you can see the tassels broke off 😢 only reason I’m giving this 4/5 stars instead of 5/5
date.of.review: Reviewed in the United States on 26 October 2023
